  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Attacking] Trash up to 2 digivolution cards from
    the bottom of 1 of your opponent's Digimon. Then, if your opponent has a Digimon
    with no digivolution cards in play, this Digimon gains \uFF1CJamming\uFF1E (This
